sh App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMI3-yTgLjrkwMVuUnyAB1H2SMdSMiuooKTq6nsaMoBBPjR0RY=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbl8tWDRKYy0tY0FFdElsSk1JLVBxalBQUVVmQXxBQ3Jtc0tucGVHTVRDZDdSSFdnZnFGWlNWeHFaZVNvbzFnOTZNZmczREUzdGMxMTZ6Y2phUjBvS0VQTmtaZnh0ZmRmaHp4YU5hRS1HRW1ON21hcDgwN0c0Y0dqYjVWYm1xbFl3MXF4RFZ6TEhuXzByMTVsWjdEVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=aNilWTBIl0g","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbl8tWDRKYy0tY0FFdElsSk1JLVBxalBQUVVmQXxBQ3Jtc0tucGVHTVRDZDdSSFdnZnFGWlNWeHFaZVNvbzFnOTZNZmczREUzdGMxMTZ6Y2phUjBvS0VQTmtaZnh0ZmRmaHp4YU5hRS1HRW1ON21hcDgwN0c0Y0dqYjVWYm1xbFl3MXF4RFZ6TEhuXzByMTVsWjdEVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=aNilWTBIl0g","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMI3-yTgLjrkwMVuUnyAB1H2SMdSMiuooKTq6nsaMoBBPjR0RY=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbEtaNkVhaGh0cEt5M25VdnVMdzM0QjhucTQ4QXxBQ3Jtc0ttMnJGaFhBc292YjV4Xzh5TEVwTmNFTUMzaVVpOTlkbFRRSnl1ZHRzOEpuZk5rTW85RlliM1Zud2tzVEVtWVFQOG5QaFZBV2YwS2hUZjFfX2tQ